  "notes": "Primary data scraped directly from the official RFEG club page (federation code MM15), which embeds full per-hole tables (Hoyo/Hdcp/Par/Metros) for all 8 rated recorridos: Blancas/Amarillas/Azules/Rojas, each rated for men and women. Internal consistency verified: men's pars sum to 72 (36/36), stroke indexes are a permutation of 1-18 (odd SI on front nine, even on back), and every tee's 18 distances sum exactly to its published total (5773/5563/5277/5165 m). Holes/par/SI above are the men's card. Ladies' card differences per RFEG: hole 7 is par 5 for women (women's par total 73); women's per-hole Hdcp allocation is identical to the men's. Cross-check with TheSocialGolfer's white-tee scorecard confirms the identical par sequence and near-identical distances (within ~5 m per hole, older card mislabeled as yards); its stroke indexes (SI 1 on hole 7 but different elsewhere) and rating (71.0/136) differ from the current official RFEG values, so RFEG figures were used. golfify.io and mscorecard.com returned HTTP 403 and could not be checked. Note: rfeg.es intermittently serves cached pages for other clubs on the same URL; the extracted page was verified to be titled CAMPOSOL CLUB DE GOLF with recorridos named CAMPOSOL."
